      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Wash, then add your<strong> spinach</strong> to a colander and pour<strong> boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p>",
