      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the spaghetti for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the spaghetti and return to the pot</p>",
