      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>creamy single soy</strong> and <strong>wilted spinach</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, most<strong> </strong>of your <strong>basil </strong>(save some for garnish), the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>plant-based creamy spinach & basil sauce</strong></p>",
